Content:: 2003 (MMIII) was a common year starting on Wednesday of the Gregorian calendar, the 2003rd year of the Common Era (CE) and Anno Domini (AD) designations, the 3rd year of the 3rd millennium and the 21st century, and the 4th year of the 2000s decade. 2003 was designated the International Year of the Fresh Water.[1] In 2003, a United States-led coalition launched the 2003 invasion of Iraq, beginning the Iraq War.
